  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110101233403\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110101233403\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>SEN&nbsp;&nbsp; 서울경제TV </p>\r\n<p>- 미즈닥터 23회 -</p>\r\n<p>&lt;&lt;내 몸의 변화 체인지&gt;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>란 프로그램입니다. </p>\r\n<p>화요일 오후 7:30분 본 방송.</p>\r\n<p>금요일 오후 7:30분 재 방송. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>-불임-이란 주제로 한방 자문을 구하기 위해 저희 한의원을 방문하셔서 촬영했습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1월 25일 화요일에 불임에 대한 방송이 나갑니다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/abfdd683042e0b2c.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110118_240/isuhani_1295329061225L6g5w_JPEG/IMG_0684.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A28B7EFB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/abfdd683042e0b2c.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/92b324f68a103c5c.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"410\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110118_287/isuhani_1295329062040VxnSQ_JPEG/IMG_0685.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A28B7EFB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/92b324f68a103c5c.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
